y of Tsar Nicholas II and Empress Alexandra.</p><button type="button" aria-label="View series" class="sc-d2a91acf-2 sc-d2a91acf-3 ejIvcK iAqLcK sc-acc23e20-10 dqliDg"><span data-testid="button-icon-wrapper" class="sc-d2a91acf-0 iFMUmd"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" category="common" icon="stack" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.88 4.51855V5.72155H18.278V15.1576H19.5V4.51855H8.88ZM6.737 6.98105V8.18405H15.797V17.2816H17.0185V6.98105H6.737ZM4.5 19.4811H14.5375V9.44355H4.5V19.4811ZM5.8345 18.1651H13.2035V10.7591H5.8345V18.1651Z"></path></svg></span><span data-testid="button-text" aria-hidden="false" class="sc-d2a91acf-1 cREArw">View series</span></button></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="ad-unit" data-component="ad-slot" class="sc-66bf5539-0 honDdn"><div data-testid="dotcom-mid_2" id="dotcom-mid_2" class="dotcom-ad"></div></div><section data-testid="virginia-section-outer-7" data-analytics-group="true" data-analytics_group_type="virginia-7" data-analytics_group_position="7" data-analytics_group_item_count="7" data-analytics_group_link="https://www.bbc.com/news" data-analytics_group_name="More news" class="sc-8fbea2e5-0 exUQHT"><div class="sc-9cd5bb24-0 lkYjpK"><div class="sc-cd6075cf-0 hZXEFS"><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 fAzFNb"><div class="sc-93f35dd3-2 dNbBzw"><div class="sc-93f35dd3-1 jFZiaU"><hr data-testid="virginia-line" class="sc-93f35dd3-0 cplrm"/></div><div data-testid="section-title-wrapper" class="sc-93f35dd3-3 bDiJPj"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="https://www.bbc.com/news" data-testid="external-anchor" target="_self" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><h2 data-testid="virginia-title" class="sc-93f35dd3-4 QbAgP">More news<svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="1em" height="1em" category="arrows" icon="chevron-right" data-testid="section-title-chevron" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M21.6 14.3 5.5 31h6.4l14.6-15L11.9 1H5.5l16.1 16.7v-3.4z"></path></svg></h2></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><section data-testid="virginia-grid-7" class="sc-9cd5bb24-0 cAWTFK"><div class="sc-cd6075cf-0 eEpsRw"><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 OpcHF"><div data-testid="london-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="london-article" class="sc-cd6075cf-0 gyStGd"><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 cuQbtT"><div class="sc-ed3b7d3e-3 ceSvPp"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/czx2gen0kwlo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-ed3b7d3e-4 lWejg"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/35fb/live/14bb0f40-4472-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.png.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Zohran Mamdani and King Charles (left); and the Koh-i-Noor diamond in the Queen Mother&#x27;s crown on the right" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 fEPSSG"><div class="sc-ed3b7d3e-0 coERwv"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/czx2gen0kwlo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-ed3b7d3e-2 lajKMJ"><div class="sc-ed3b7d3e-1 jfHkFA"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 kEkvUR">Mamdani says he would ask King Charles to return Koh-i-Noor</h2></div></div><p class="sc-ed3b7d3e-5 gEYBZu">New York&#x27;s mayor made the comments hours before meeting King Charles, but it&#x27;s unclear if he brought up the diamond.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">2 hrs ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">World</span></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 cKhECM"><div class="sc-cd6075cf-0 rQgu"><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 fQkOKX"><div data-testid="dundee-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/c5y9wlnwl85o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="dundee-article" class="sc-329e5f2b-1 gnGpEW"><div data-testid="card-image-wrapper" class="sc-329e5f2b-3 kkqTyl"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-329e5f2b-4 eASWcB"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="25vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Statue  of a man holding a flag in central  London. A London bus and people walking around  in the background" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-fa53feb6-0 hnNPal"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa">Statue with Banksy&#x27;s signature appears in London</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-329e5f2b-0 ffnHHm">A sculpture of a man marching off a plinth in St James&#x27;s appears to bear the artist&#x27;s name.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">26 mins ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">London</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 dLsRZu"><div data-testid="manchester-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/c4gv4dvngygo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="manchester-article" class="sc-548b08f-1 gnBgeL"><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-548b08f-2 hvtsmL"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa">China to ban drone sales in Beijing citing security concerns</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-548b08f-0 cValTX">Drone users will also be required to register their devices and secure permits before flying them.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">5 hrs ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">Asia</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 gHHaTH"><div data-testid="manchester-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/c4g4lk9m77vo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="manchester-article" class="sc-548b08f-1 gnBgeL"><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-548b08f-2 hvtsmL"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa">Israel intercepts Gaza flotilla near Crete and detains 175 activists</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-548b08f-0 cValTX">Pro-Palestinian activists say 22 boats carrying aid for Gaza were illegally intercepted in international waters near the Greek island.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">2 hrs ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">World</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 juzRmN"><div data-testid="dundee-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/clyplg23l30o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="dundee-article" class="sc-329e5f2b-1 gnGpEW"><div data-testid="card-image-wrapper" class="sc-329e5f2b-3 kkqTyl"><div data-testid="card-media" class="s