estid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">World</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 jvSSAX"><div data-testid="dundee-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/cpqpzlrd3wwo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="dundee-article" class="sc-329e5f2b-1 gnGpEW"><div data-testid="card-image-wrapper" class="sc-329e5f2b-3 kkqTyl"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-329e5f2b-4 eASWcB"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="25vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/2720/live/47c46aa0-4416-11f1-9fe7-21f79f0ffc75.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Mexican police at the scene of a murder in Sinaloa" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-fa53feb6-0 hnNPal"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa">US charges Mexican governor and other leaders with aiding drug cartel</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-329e5f2b-0 ffnHHm">The governor of Sinaloa, Rubén Rocha Moya, hails from the same party as the president of Mexico.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">7 hrs ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">World</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-82b3c53b-0 ldcLJX"><div data-testid="dundee-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/articles/cdjpw0n889yo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="dundee-article" class="sc-329e5f2b-1 gnGpEW"><div data-testid="card-image-wrapper" class="sc-329e5f2b-3 kkqTyl"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-329e5f2b-4 eASWcB"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="25vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/283d/live/261df4e0-443c-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Three women with blonde hair look at floral tributes" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-fa53feb6-0 hnNPal"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 eQumHa">Jewish agency warned of &#x27;high&#x27; threat level ahead of Bondi shooting, report finds </h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-329e5f2b-0 ffnHHm">Gun reforms should be prioritised and policing around Jewish events increased, royal commission says.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-lastupdated" class="sc-1907e52a-1 bZuSaP">4 hrs ago</span><div data-testid="card-metadata-separator" class="sc-1907e52a-3 hCbeEG"></div><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 dIrLFx">Australia</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></section></section><section data-testid="texas-section-outer" data-analytics-group="true" data-analytics_group_type="texas-8" data-analytics_group_position="8" data-analytics_group_item_count="8" data-analytics_group_link="https://www.bbc.com/video" data-analytics_group_name="Must watch" class="sc-137e23a3-1 hrUyPQ"><div data-testid="texas-section" class="sc-137e23a3-2 bHibBM"><div class="sc-93f35dd3-2 kDYKbZ"><div class="sc-93f35dd3-1 jFZiaU"><hr data-testid="texas-line" class="sc-93f35dd3-0 gxzoAS"/></div><div data-testid="section-title-wrapper" class="sc-93f35dd3-3 boOqBM"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="https://www.bbc.com/video" data-testid="external-anchor" target="_self" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><h2 data-testid="texas-title" class="sc-93f35dd3-4 iWHuRZ">Must watch<svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="1em" height="1em" category="arrows" icon="chevron-right" data-testid="section-title-chevron" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M21.6 14.3 5.5 31h6.4l14.6-15L11.9 1H5.5l16.1 16.7v-3.4z"></path></svg></h2></a></div></div></div><div data-testid="texas-grid" class="sc-c64a065b-0 dbmcvm"><div class="sc-c64a065b-1 fKKSTF"><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/ce9pj2ygmkno" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/3803/live/25879b90-442c-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Splitscreen. Left, Camilla reads a book to kids. Right, Charles and a small child plant vegetables with a trowel. " class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">The King and Queen in the Big Apple: What the royals did on their third day in the US</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">After visiting the 9/11 Memorial, Queen Camilla read to children at the New York Public Library and King Charles visited a community organisation in Harlem.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">US &amp; Canada</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/reel/video/p0myl6m3/watch" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/160x90/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 160w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/240x135/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/320x180/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/480x270/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/640x360/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 640w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/800x450/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1024x576/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 1024w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1376x774/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 1376w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1920x1080/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp 1920w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/480x270/p0mylgmh.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Chris Hemsworth&#x27;s deeply emotional journey across Australia with his father" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">Chris Hemsworth&#x27;s deeply emotional journey with his father</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">Chris Hemsworth tells Graham Norton how he made a documentary about his dad&#x27;s Alzheimer&#x27;s treatment.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">Film &amp; TV</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/cvgzlpzglx2o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1258/live/9eb8eda0-442e-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Mineral Wells, Texas, lies destroyed in a drone shot post-tornado." class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">Aerial video shows destruction after tornado strikes small Texas town</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">A severe storm outbreak has been battering parts of the Midwest and Southern United States for nearly a week. </p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">US &amp; Canada</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/cglpkexdye1o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/b7bd/live/0e216ca0-4450-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="A performer in traditional dress grins as she dances." class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">Joy as Kenya&#x27;s record-breaking runner Sabastian Sawe returns home</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">BBC reports from Kenya, home to Sabastian Sawe, the first man to run a marathon in under two hours.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">Africa</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/c332ng27x1jo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1d63/live/a6477a00-43c0-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="The King grins at Trump from the lectern as the president looks in his direction" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">&#x27;If it wasn&#x27;t for us, you&#x27;d be speaking French&#x27;: King and Trump joke at dinner</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">The King and the US president exchanged several jokes during their speeches at a state banquet.
</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">US &amp; Canada</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/cpdpql7d839o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/a36b/live/fdf2dbd0-43d6-11f1-bf3e-3d07e81b01ce.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Lucy Williamson in Jerusalem" class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">There&#x27;s a ceasefire in Lebanon - but the fighting hasn&#x27;t stopped</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">Israel and Hezbollah are still fighting in Lebanon despite a US-brokered ceasefire that began 12 days ago.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">Middle East</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/c87qg28rx8jo" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img src="https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260427-074339-4d487e3684-web-3.2.0-4/grey-placeholder.png" class="sc-5340b511-0 gUePlo hide-when-no-script" aria-label="image unavailable"/><img sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1008px) 25vw, (min-width: 800px) 33vw, 50vw" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp 1536w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/5e8b/live/50fa4df0-4372-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg.webp" loading="lazy" alt="BBC&#x27;s Regan Morris in a split screen with Jimmy Kimmel." class="sc-5340b511-0 hLdNfA"/></div></div><div data-testid="content-type-label" class="sc-3430e63c-0 cKCAIY"><div data-testid="content-type-icon-wrapper" class="sc-3430e63c-1 guoqgi"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="30" height="30" category="playback-avkx" icon="play" type="playback-avkx:play" class="sc-583246d7-0 jUqtCV"><path d="M29 16 5.8 1v30L29 16z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div data-testid="card-text-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-3 VIGhh"><div class="sc-feaf8701-1 dzYnRP"><div class="sc-feaf8701-0 ktNWyK"><h2 data-testid="card-headline" class="sc-feaf8701-3 goAeMP">Should Jimmy Kimmel be fired for telling a joke?</h2></div></div><p data-testid="card-description" class="sc-8a86ca4a-4 kEJoCh">BBC&#x27;s Regan Morris reports from outside the comedian&#x27;s show on Hollywood Boulevard, Los Angeles.</p><div class="sc-1907e52a-0 jkvOKk"><span data-testid="card-metadata-tag" class="sc-1907e52a-2 coRVrA">Culture</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-c64a065b-2 fiRPhe"><div data-testid="edinburgh-card" data-indexcard="true" class="sc-225578b-0 ezQaGx"><div data-testid="anchor-inner-wrapper"><a href="/news/videos/cz92wdvwek8o" data-testid="internal-link" class="sc-8a623a54-0 huZCWi"><div data-testid="edinburgh-video" class="sc-8a86ca4a-0 fsZVWy"><div data-testid="card-media-wrapper" class="sc-8a86ca4a-1 cazend"><div data-testid="card-media" class="sc-8a86ca4a-2 bWlUxl"><div class="sc-5340b511-1 cMIbKV"><img