ags":[],"description":"The mother of Shloime Rand, 34, says she hopes her son will be home from hospital for Shabbat on Friday. The other victim has been named as Moshe Shine, 76.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/333d/live/91ee53d0-446f-11f1-97e2-ede52d59c1ad.png","altText":"Body-worn footage showing a police officer's arm holding a Taser, another officer to the left and the knife suspect walking towards them","width":1283,"height":721}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:tipo:topic:c3ve2nr60xzt","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Oil price hits highest since 2022 after report Trump to be briefed on new Iran options","href":"/news/articles/cx21m88rd14o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777544444416,"firstUpdated":1777521961656,"topics":["Business"]},"tags":[],"description":"Axios reported that US Central Command has prepared a plan for a wave of \"short and powerful\" strikes on Iran.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/f095/live/e9ca4ae0-442a-11f1-84a0-55946b952877.jpg","altText":"A female petrol station attendant refuels a white car","width":875,"height":492}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cx21m88rd14o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"'Attacked 28 times in a day': BBC visits heavily targeted US-UK base in Iraq","href":"/news/videos/c5y9wdprpyyo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"video","subtype":"clip news","lastUpdated":1777513612702,"firstUpdated":1777513205062,"topics":["US \u0026 Canada"]},"tags":[],"description":"Before the fragile ceasefire in the region, this was one of the most heavily targeted US and UK military bases in the Middle East.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/0976/live/9ae859a0-445a-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg","altText":"Soldier putting missile in tube","width":1677,"height":944}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:c5y9wdprpyyo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Police say they believe abducted child was murdered as body found in Outback","href":"/news/articles/cvgzd1yp2n6o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777530595520,"firstUpdated":1777524855410,"topics":["Australia"]},"tags":[],"description":"The five-year-old girl was last seen on Saturday at an Aboriginal town camp near Alice Springs. ","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/25a4/live/83eee950-41d8-11f1-8c86-d995ee1a7acb.jpg","altText":"An Aboriginal girl wearing a pink dress and blue backpack poses for a picture, holding up the peace sign","width":502,"height":282}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cvgzd1yp2n6o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"The 'Polar Bear Capital' with Arctic gateway ambitions","href":"/news/articles/cyv1zdey7pmo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777505730959,"firstUpdated":1777505730959,"topics":["US \u0026 Canada"]},"tags":[],"description":"Canada is weighing whether a year-round northern trade route to Europe from Churchill, Manitoba, is viable, as climate change speeds Arctic warming.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/8557/live/a143aa40-43f9-11f1-a314-cde9f81d6d3e.jpg","altText":"An image of Mike Pence, mayor of Churchill. He is wearing a black 'The North Face' puffer jacket. Behind him is the Port of Churchill blanketed with snow, and a clear blue sky above. He is looking towards the left.","width":4240,"height":2385}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cyv1zdey7pmo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Have the royals got their mojo back from US visit?","href":"/news/articles/cqxpr404053o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777520933199,"firstUpdated":1777520933199,"topics":["UK"]},"tags":[],"description":"Many commentators, even critics of the monarchy, seem delighted at the spectacle. ","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/15f6/live/1b425cd0-445c-11f1-ac78-2112837ce2aa.jpg","altText":"The King and Queen descend the stairs from their aircraft with the UK flag in view,as they arrive at the start of the their US trip.","width":1920,"height":1080}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cqxpr404053o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Smiles and wonder: How the US reacted to King Charles ","href":"/news/articles/ce8pd1kr387o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777499032319,"firstUpdated":1777499032319,"topics":["US \u0026 Canada"]},"tags":[],"description":"A divided US has come together to watch King Charles' visit with a mix of awe, delight and hope. ","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/c73a/live/809bce40-446b-11f1-ac78-2112837ce2aa.jpg","altText":"King Charles laughing as he greets peope in New York. Pictured with a happy man who looks at the camera with big smile. ","width":1856,"height":1044}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:ce8pd1kr387o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""}],"collectionId":"news-home-top-stories-us-tipo","sectionTitleProps":{},"paginationData":{"page":0,"pageSize":7,"total":13},"title":"","summary":"","disableAutoPlay":false,"innerCollections":[],"playlistMode":false},{"type":"advertisement","model":{"adType":"horizontal"},"incrementedType":"mid_1"},{"type":"indiana","content":[{"title":"AI is finding 'hidden sperm' in men deemed infertile","href":"/future/article/20260429-finding-hidden-sperm-new-technology-offers-hope-to-men-previously-told-they-were-infertile","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"features","lastUpdated":1777541563932,"firstUpdated":1777541563932,"topics":["Future"]},"tags":[],"description":"Millions of men experience azoospermia, where they produce little to no sperm. A new AI-powered technique is giving fresh hope to couples looking to have children.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1920xn/p0nh9j4l.jpg","altText":"Illustration of a sperm cell being injected into an egg during in vitro fertilisation (Credit: Getty Images)","width":1920,"height":1080}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:pubpipe:wwverticals:article:future/article/20260429-finding-hidden-sperm-new-technology-offers-hope-to-men-previously-told-they-were-infertile","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Dutton Ranch to Lord of the Flies: 11 of the best TV shows to watch in May","href":"/culture/article/20260427-11-of-the-best-tv-shows-to-watch-this-may","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"features","lastUpdated":1777544513701,"firstUpdated":1777544513701,"topics":["Culture"]},"tags":[],"description":"From the latest Yellowstone spin-off to a new take on William Golding's classic novel about violent schoolboys – these are the best series to watch and stream.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1920xn/p0ngv9g7.jpg","altText":"Kelly Reilly and Cole Hauser dancing together in Dutton Ranch (Credit: Paramount)","width":2200,"height":1467}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:pubpipe:wwverticals:article:culture/article/20260427-11-of-the-best-tv-shows-to-watch-this-may","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""}],"c