isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777544229231,"firstUpdated":1777537389925,"topics":["London"]},"tags":[],"description":"A sculpture of a man marching off a plinth in St James's appears to bear the artist's name.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/574a/live/1b434ec0-447e-11f1-98f4-457ce687c58a.jpg","altText":"Statue  of a man holding a flag in central  London. A London bus and people walking around  in the background","width":1560,"height":878}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:c5y9wlnwl85o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Trump says US studying troop cuts in Germany, after Merz criticises war","href":"/news/articles/clyplg23l30o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777519551567,"firstUpdated":1777519551567,"topics":["World"]},"tags":[],"description":"His remarks come after the German chancellor criticised the US approach to the war in Iran.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/eb90/live/a5b0c260-443b-11f1-adcb-799f507df11c.jpg","altText":"Six US soldiers in green camouflage uniforms are pictured in Germany standing in a circle, with a long line of military vehicles visible behind them.","width":1024,"height":576}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:clyplg23l30o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"US charges Mexican governor and other leaders with aiding drug cartel","href":"/news/articles/cpqpzlrd3wwo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777519204623,"firstUpdated":1777507215373,"topics":["World"]},"tags":[],"description":"The governor of Sinaloa, Rubén Rocha Moya, hails from the same party as the president of Mexico.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"sr