back whale inside a boat","width":1908,"height":1073}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:clyp559l06no","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Meta in row after workers who say they saw smart glasses users having sex lose jobs","href":"/news/articles/c5y7yvgy0w6o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777539575202,"firstUpdated":1777539575202,"topics":["Africa"]},"tags":[],"description":"Meta and its subcontractor disagree over why over 1000 Kenya-based workers were made redundant.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/6037/live/f8d385c0-4307-11f1-8d32-27ce5a537ca2.jpg","altText":"Meta boss Mark Zuckerberg - puts on thick rimmed meta smart glasses. Zuckerberg has medium length blond curly hair and has visible stubble.","width":1024,"height":576}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:c5y7yvgy0w6o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Robert Mugabe's son deported from South Africa over firearms offence","href":"/news/articles/czx2lxevvljo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777537639871,"firstUpdated":1777466318296,"topics":["Africa"]},"tags":[],"description":"The 28-year-old was arrested in February after a man had been shot at his home in Johannesburg.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/fc56/live/0dc03f70-43c4-11f1-a0e9-f392511be4c3.jpg","altText":"Close-up of Bellarmine Mugabe. The partial black and white collar and black shoulders of his jacket can be seen. He is standing indoors.","width":1007,"height":566}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:czx2lxevvljo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""}],"sectionTitleProps":{"link":"https://www.bbc.com/news/world","linkType":"internal"}},{"title":"Business","data":[{"title":"What's happening to UK petrol and diesel prices?","href":"/news/articles/c20zgjzz0e4o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777539172828,"firstUpdated":1772457119011,"topics":["Business"]},"tags":[],"description":"UK petrol and diesel prices have started to fall after 46 consecutive days of rises at the pump.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/26f2/live/5fbf6110-2e5d-11f1-9408-ab8675603e32.jpg","altText":"A stock photo of lady in a brown jacket filling up her car with fuel at a petrol station.","width":2070,"height":1165}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:c20zgjzz0e4o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"'We will kill you and burn your house': Council staff under attack from High Street gangs","href":"/news/articles/cdxplq92rx1o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777525204995,"firstUpdated":1777525204995,"topics":["Business"]},"tags":[],"description":"Dozens of Trading Standards officers describe intimidation from criminals running mini-marts and vape shops.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/d9fb/live/ec24e4c0-430e-11f1-ac78-2112837ce2aa.jpg","altText":"Mandy has short dark hair, is wearing a dark textured jacket and small drop earrings, and is turned slightly to one side with the face in profile.","width":1920,"height":1080}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cdxplq92rx1o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Meta shares slide as plan to spend billions more on AI spooks investors","href":"/news/articles/crkpd4r2y7eo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777510127059,"firstUpdated":1777498901495,"topics":["Business"]},"tags":[],"description":"Other tech giants Alphabet, Microsoft and Amazon also reported quarterly earnings on Wednesday.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/290b/live/2b798220-4472-11f1-b545-b533bcf4cad2.jpg","altText":"Meta boss Mark Zuckerberg looking down","width":1024,"height":576}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:crkpd4r2y7eo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"A son overlooked and a jailed tycoon: Inside Samsung's succession drama","href":"/news/articles/c9d313g91g4o","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777504904223,"firstUpdated":1777502153259,"topics":["Business"]},"tags":[],"description":"The family dynasty behind Samsung is so complicated it regularly makes headline news in South Korea.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/733a/live/0970f1e0-4369-11f1-bd5c-f7e837bf2c66.jpg","altText":"Lee Jae-yong, chairman of Samsung Electronics Co., arrives at the Seoul Central District Court in Seoul, South Korea, on Monday, 5 Feb., 2024. ","width":820,"height":461}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:c9d313g91g4o","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""}],"sectionTitleProps":{"link":"https://www.bbc.com/business","linkType":"internal"}},{"title":"Technology","data":[{"title":"Women can wait years for an endometriosis diagnosis. New tech could change that","href":"/news/articles/clyplwvgxjvo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777507739998,"firstUpdated":1777507739998,"topics":["Health"]},"tags":[],"description":"A new scan technique could spot areas of endometriosis missed by conventional scans, scientists in the UK say.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/a852/live/6c3989f0-4462-11f1-ac78-2112837ce2aa.jpg","altText":"Stock image of woman with curly brown shoulder length hair sitting on a grey softa. Her arms are folded over her abdomen and she appears to be grimacing and upset in pain. She wears a terracotta shirt and green trousers. There is light coming in through a nearby window. ","width":1920,"height":1080}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:clyplwvgxjvo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Why AI companies want you to be afraid of them","href":"/future/article/20260428-ai-companies-want-you-to-be-afraid-of-them","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"features","lastUpdated":1777456800000,"firstUpdated":1777456800000,"topics":["Future"]},"tags":[],"description":"A tech company says it has built a new AI that's so powerful it's too dangerous to release into the world – luckily for us, they're keeping it locked up for now. They just wanted you to know.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1920xn/p0nh5hny.jpg","altText":"Several hands hold computer windows with \"X\" and exclamation point warning signs over a desktop screen that says \"AI\" (Credit: Serenity Strull/ BBC/ Getty Images)","width":1442,"height":812}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:pubpipe:wwverticals:article:future/article/20260428-ai-companies-want-you-to-be-afraid-of-them","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Why Sam Altman and his former hero Elon Musk are taking their toxic feud to court","href":"/news/articles/cn8dedv8w8xo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777390689345,"firstUpdated":1777371054611,"topics":[]},"tags":[],"description":"The battle between the AI big hitters has largely played out on social media. Now it is coming to the courtroom.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/2441/live/9eec0d50-4246-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.png","altText":"Stylised image showing Elon Musk on the left against an orange background and Sam Altman on the right against a bright blue background, with a white lightning strike line in between them and a picture of a gavel in the middle.","width":1920,"height":1080}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cn8dedv8w8xo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""},{"title":"Japan Airlines trials humanoid robots as ground handlers","href":"/news/articles/cpwp87j1llvo","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"article","subtype":"news","lastUpdated":1777370626095,"firstUpdated":1777370626095,"topics":["Asia"]},"tags":[],"description":"These robots may in future help clean cabins and operate ground support equipment.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"blocks":{"src":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/7dbc/live/49291220-4302-11f1-b538-f34ed0c59bce.jpg","altText":"A humanoid robot pushes a cargo container during a media demonstration at Haneda airport in Tokyo on April 27, 2026. Japan Airlines will test the use of such robots at the airport from May, as the airline aims for their practical use in ground handling tasks, such as cargo loading and unloading, in 2028 amid a chronic manpower shortage","width":1911,"height":1075}}},"relatedUrls":[],"id":"urn:bbc:optimo:asset:cpwp87j1llvo","brandName":"","seriesName":"","seriesId":"","brandId":"","versionId":""}],"sectionTitleProps":{"link":"https://www.bbc.com/technology","linkType":"internal"}}],"playlistMode":false},{"type":"iowa","content":[{"title":"Champions Cup: The big semi-final preview with Henry Arundell","href":"/audio/play/p0nhfl2d","isLiveNow":false,"metadata":{"contentType":"episode","subtype":"episode","lastUpdated":1777507200000,"firstUpdated":1777507200000,"topics":[],"duration":3057},"tags":[],"description":"Chris and Ashy preview the Champions Cup semi-finals with Bath’s Henry Arundell.","image":{"type":"indexImage","model":{"bl